@Coin Game@
> Play
  Info
  Quit
(press 'W' / 'UP' & 'S' / 'DOWN' to go trough the options; press 'ENTER' / 'E' to select)
#Game Modes#
> 2 Players
  Player & Bot
  Player & MAX Bot
  Player & Smart Bot
  Right player starts: OFF
  Blindfold mode: OFF
  Max coin value: 15
  Number of coins: 8
  Back
!Info!
Game by Tuchel Andrei for Computer Science Qualification Project.

Rules:
-Each game has a number of "coins" with randomised values put in a row.
-A player can choose between the first and last coin form the row.
-The game ends when there are no more coins left.
-The winner is the player with the highest score.

Game controls:
-P1: 'A' and 'D' to move and 'E' to select a coin
-P2: Left and Right Arrow to move and 'ENTER' to select a coin


Blindfold game mode:
-The players can't see the coins' values until the game ends

> Back
